sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as Database<br/>(PostgreSQL/MariaDB)<br/>TLS optional
    participant PVC as PVC Storage

    Note over Client,PVC: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service API Request

    Client->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS termination
    Route->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (reencrypt)
    KRBP->>KRBP: TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    KRBP->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    TAS->>DB: TCP/varies<br/>TLS optional, Username/Password
    TAS->>PVC: Filesystem I/O<br/>(alternative storage)
    TAS-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    participant User as User/kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant JobPod as LMEvalJob Pod
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,HF: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch notification
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>JobPod: Pod scheduled
    JobPod->>HF: Download model/dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>JobPod: Model artifacts
    JobPod->>JobPod: Run evaluation
    LMESCtrl->>JobPod: Pod exec (status)<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    JobPod-->>LMESCtrl: Evaluation results
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob status

    participant GClient as Client
    participant GRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GKRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP
    participant Detector as Detector<br/>InferenceServices

    Note over GClient,Detector: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator Request

    GClient->>GRoute: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS
    GRoute->>GKRBP: HTTPS/8432<br/>TLS (reencrypt)
    GKRBP->>GKRBP: TokenReview<br/>(conditional)
    GKRBP->>Orch: HTTP/8032<br/>internal
    Orch->>Detector: HTTPS/varies<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>GKRBP: Orchestrated response
    GKRBP-->>GRoute: HTTPS Response
    GRoute-->>GClient: HTTPS Response

    participant EClient as Client
    participant ERoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EHub as EvalHub<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EDB as PostgreSQL<br/>(optional)
    participant EPod as Evaluation Pods<br/>(tenant namespaces)

    Note over EClient,EPod: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation

    EClient->>ERoute: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS
    ERoute->>EHub: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (reencrypt)
    EHub->>EDB: TCP/varies<br/>TLS, DB credentials
    EHub->>EPod: Create via K8s API<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    EPod-->>EHub: Evaluation results
    EHub-->>ERoute: HTTPS Response
    ERoute-->>EClient: HTTPS Response
